These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, horse
There 2 different types of food: pepper, nectarine
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, italian
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the italian##3
2. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
3. the person eating nectarine is the owner of the snake##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Pet      | snake  | horse   |
| Food   | nectarine     | pepper   |
| Nationality         | italian | japanese |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
House: cape-cod, art-deco
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, emerald
2 different games are played: domino, snooker
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes apricot is the person driving the tram##1
3. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| House          | cape-cod     | art-deco |
| Color   | emerald | apricot  |
| Game           | snooker         | domino     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
House: futuristic, craftsman
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, fishing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, d&b
1. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| House         | craftsman | futuristic    |
| Hobby         | skydiving         | fishing        |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop         | d&b    |

