.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
City: london, san-francisco
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, parkour
2 different pets are kept: goat, cat
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
3. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| City      | san-francisco     | london |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| Sport         | water-polo | parkour     |
| Pet   | goat  | cat         |

