.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
2 different games are played: backgammon, whist
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, tiparillo
2 different pets are kept: cat, horse
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing whist is the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Game           | whist | backgammon    |
| Cigar   | vegafina       | tiparillo |
| Pet           | cat         | horse    |
| Hobby         | chess    | skydiving   |

