.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, thriller
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, snowboarding
City: miami, venice
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller        | documentary |
| Sport         | baseball          | snowboarding     |
| City   | miami        | venice     |

 